name: Morris
content:
Morris was a Human male smuggler fence who operated out of the Nightsister Stronghold on the planet Dathomir during the time of the Galactic Civil War.
Morris was a non-player character in the 2003 video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online roleplaying game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011. Morris was added to the game along with the smuggling missions introduced with the "Chapter 3" update, released on September 27, 2006.
